***Call or text (760) 533-0532 for an exclusive showing***

*** Tours available every day! Call (760) 533-0532 to schedule your tour now. ***

*Do not get stuck owning two homes. BUY THIS HOME, WE WILL BUY YOURS! If you are looking to buy a home but have one to sell, you are finding yourself in the same dilemma that most homeowners find themselves in. We can help! To discuss the details of this incredible option, Call or text (760) 533-0532.

*************************************************
 
VIEWS VIEWS VIEWS! SINGLE STORY, RV PARKING! Get ready to escape to your own desert oasis. This fully furnished home sits on over an acre of flat usable land. You are greeted by 23 Jacaranda trees that adorn the front of the home and create the ultimate private retreat. The driveway is completely paved allowing for RV parking, ample parking for other vehicles, and parking in the attached 2 car garage. Have peace of mind knowing this home is centrally located within 2 minutes of the helicopter pad that can take you to the nearby medical facility. You will enjoy all the activities available to you at the Rams Hill country club. Stay active with swimming, pickle ball and more. There is a large, enclosed dog run or play area on the side of the home. The layout provides the opportunity for an AirBNB or rental. The master bedroom is on its own private wing with a private entrance. The remaining 2 guest rooms are located on the other wing and have their own entrance as well. There is also a den that can be converted to a 4th bedroom or office. Beautiful wood flooring throughout along with tile flooring to keep the house nice and cool. The kitchen is spacious with beautiful custom cabinetry. Conveniently clean your home using the Central vacuum. There is also a spacious 2 car garage with plenty of storage throughout. But hurry! Homes this special don’t last long! 

*************************************************

BUY ANY HOME FROM US AND IF YOU ARE NOT COMPLETELY SATISFIED WE WILL BUY IT BACK. For more information on this Peace of Mind Guarantee Call The Jim Bottrell Team® directly at (760) 533-0532. The Jim Bottrell Team® * Ardent Real Estate Services® * DRE: 01154905 *Some Conditions Apply.*
